WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
This is an end story. There are so many things that you guys do that we are never going to

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:13.440
do, and there are things that we do really, really well. And so, you know, this is a chance

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:18.440
for folks to just get a nice, seamless experience and then just start realizing the value out

00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:19.440
of their data.

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:24.920
Yeah, it's very complimentary. We provide a great data and AI platform. We provide some

00:00:24.920 --> 00:00:30.520
awesome tools for developers on top of that platform, and you have great general tools

00:00:30.520 --> 00:00:35.919
for data scientists overall in all languages. And I think that combination is fantastic.

